    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎴 <strong>Yaku Slap</strong> – Walk the Flower Path and Slap Down Monsters! 🌸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to duel monsters, master ancient card combos, and get <i>just</i> a little addicted to slapping down the perfect hand? <strong>Yaku Slap</strong> blends the strategic flair of <i>Hanafuda Koi Koi</i> with rogue-like chaos where every match could be your last—or your ultimate victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful spells, master rare <strong>Yaku</strong> combinations, and score big as you fight your way down the <strong>Flower Path</strong> to become a true <strong>Yaku Master</strong>. Win, lose, and unlock classes, and passive abilities with every run!<br><br>🎴 <strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Strategic Card Combat:</strong> Master the classic <i>Koi Koi</i> mechanics with a supernatural twist.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸 <strong>Rogue-like Progression:</strong> Every run earns you perks and passives to power up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250410/extras/d4da35eec90be9c0f93fac1ab55850ec.avif?t=1749509655\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250410/extras_big/d4da35eec90be9c0f93fac1ab55850ec.avif?t=1749509655 width=800 height=548 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏 <strong>Monster Showdowns:</strong> Duel dangerous creatures that are as challenging as they are zany—slap hard or get slapped!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250410/extras/0cfd9cfc818768fe622027d5a8822891.avif?t=1749509655\" width=643 height=686 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Endless Replayability:</strong> Spells, items, and split cards keep every playthrough fresh.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250410/extras/e5e5df112afbbd7311d6f24fe8979ed4.avif?t=1749509655\" width=800 height=986 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😈 <strong>Cheeky Humor &amp; Style:</strong> Relaxing vibes meet monster-smacking fun.</p></li></ul>",
